er, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67158c79d0981cac54d662a73bec35c0c50621d4","tid":1506783,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:25:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd6a9d04d982bc7d68b21785d446ee44fc716503","tid":1506783,"uid":55130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:26:26.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦 老鼠成"},{"pid":"5541a999e2b8cb2f09e638c0f0168fe8c5d2696e","tid":1506783,"uid":28558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"八股到仆街<br />\n一句話講完好冇? <br />\n就係官迫民反"},{"pid":"9124178820cc30ccfa30bcb5aa34ce30706d5d47","tid":1506783,"uid":64636,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"957e40eed48b1d282158808a29d77454984820ba","tid":1506783,"uid":4574,"like":58,"dislike":5,"score":53,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"仲以為有乜<br />\n真知灼見<br />\n<br />\n失望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:38:06.000Z","msg":"一個十三歲小